<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>2025-04 on WHY的博客空间</title><link>https://wanghaoyang1995.github.io/archives/2025-04/</link><description>Recent content in 2025-04 on WHY的博客空间</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2025 23:29:52 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://wanghaoyang1995.github.io/archives/2025-04/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>射线交叉法判断点是否位于几何体内部</title><link>https://wanghaoyang1995.github.io/posts/graphics/ray_casting/</link><pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 23:51:57 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://wanghaoyang1995.github.io/posts/graphics/ray_casting/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>射线交叉法&lt;/strong>可以用来计算一点是否在几何体内部，在本文中用于初始化有符号距离场的符号。其思路是，从网格内每一个点开始，沿x轴正向（沿任意一个方向均可）发出一条射线，判断这条射线穿过几何表面的次数，奇数次为内部点，偶数次为外部点。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>